{"tid":1564742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［經濟永續］文宣派發計劃上線，召派發專員，腦細","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:54:28.000Z","uid":81231,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"696d7a34597b697d717a935951fa9fa1c78ffd6c","tid":1564742,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">良心企業上線了。<br />\n</span><br />\n點解街邊阿姐派放題388傳單有錢收，我地派文宣無？<br />\n點解做老麥得幾十蚊個鐘，又無意義，我地唔去派文宣？<br />\n點解咁多人做左咁多文宣，又無人知？<br />\n點解咁多仆街企業幾十蚊都拖糧？<br />\n<br />\n大家好有熱情去推動運動，但係，要行落去，我地除左繼續參與，參與係最重要，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地都要響經濟、生活等等支持自己同路人</span>，推動民主運動繼續向前。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">形式</span>：<br />\n認投式。派發專員tg 我地派發內容建議，並負責印刷。建議會馬上forward到腦細tg, 腦細們快快手認投，一星期內出糧。例如：<br />\n<br />\n地區：黃大仙<br />\n數量：A4雙面300張<br />\n金額：600（派工）+300（印刷）<br />\n備註：現金出糧<br />\n<br />\n想印文宣貼街貼連襛，我地一樣接受！請tg我地。<br />\n地區：黃大仙<br />\n數量：A4雙面300張<br />\n金額：300（印刷）+ 物資<br />\n備註：現金出糧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依個唔係資助計劃，依個係一份工，一份派傳單既工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n安全問題，三人成團。唔好一個人響街派呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>腦細、派發專員請tg：<a href=\"https://t.me/yourparents\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyourparents&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=9c3223a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yourparents</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"01f237911f1a66e733243cf93d7db1f8319b7069","tid":1564742,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3d3ff216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"d34795486e9222f6f9821301aca22cd8f0100020","tid":1564742,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1da49c5f1b039133ad07706c3eb755a4997daee5","tid":1564742,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bf1e7c14cf1996c44b66d6e245a250b600673251","tid":1564742,"uid":208452,"l